author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Cracked shower tile removal tips…I remove the grout then use a hammer to carefully smash the tile. I also use a chisel to remove tile shards from the waterproofing. No doubt, this takes patience and attention to detail. All the supplies I use fit into the Milwaukee Packout Backpack which is great for projects like this 🔥#tileremoval #bathroomrenovation #whatareyouworkingon #homerepairtutor
